</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Templater_NewTemplateMulti.svg|32px]] '''Templater NewTemplateMulti''' tool creates a small example template and inserts it as a new drawing page into the active document.
</div>

